arStrings.szText: "I found Sihek and helped him in his task. What else do you need?"
Ormus thanks you for your efforts. Now we must turn our attention outside of the walls of Kurast. There is an ancient force that you may already know.
Mysterious, yes, but we would do well to make an ally of it. If you are to be prepared for the torments ahead, seek the favor of the Tree of Whispers.
